{"id":832,"parent_id":828,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":832,"title":"Ezekiel 4","subtitle":"","short_title":"Ezek.","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/4","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 4"],[".studySummary",["i","Ezekiel symbolically illustrates the siege and famine that will befall Jerusalem."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/4.1","order":"02.27.004.55166"},["b","1"],"Thou also, son of man, take thee",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"a tile"],", and lay it before thee, and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"portray"],"upon it the city,",["i","even"],"Jerusalem:"],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/4.2","order":"02.27.004.55167"},["b","2"],"And",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"lay siege against it"],", and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_2b"},"build"],"a fort against it, and",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_2c"},"cast"],"a",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_2d"},"mount"],"against it; set the camp also against it, and set",["i",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_2e"},"battering"]],"rams against it round about."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/4.3","order":"02.27.004.55168"},["b","3"],"Moreover take thou unto thee an iron pan, and set it",["i","for"],"a wall of iron between thee and the city: and set thy face against it, and it shall be besieged, and thou shalt lay siege against it. This",["i","shall be"],"a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"sign"],"to the house of Israel."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/4.4","order":"02.27.004.55169"},["b","4"],"Lie thou also upon thy left side, and lay the iniquity of the house of Israel upon it:",["i","according"],"to the number of the days that thou shalt lie upon it thou shalt bear their iniquity."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/4.5","order":"02.27.004.55170"},["b","5"],"For I have laid upon thee the years of their iniquity, according to the number of the days, three hundred and ninety days: so shalt thou bear the iniquity of the house of Israel."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/4.6","order":"02.27.004.55171"},["b","6"],"And when thou hast accomplished them, lie again on thy right side, and thou shalt bear the iniquity of the house of Judah forty days: I have appointed thee each day for a year."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/4.7","order":"02.27.004.55172"},["b","7"],"Therefore thou shalt set thy face toward the siege of Jerusalem, and thine arm",["i","shall be"],"uncovered, and thou shalt prophesy against it."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/4.8","order":"02.27.004.55173"},["b","8"],"And, behold, I will lay bands upon thee, and thou shalt not turn thee from one side to another, till thou hast ended the days of thy siege."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/4.9","order":"02.27.004.55174"},["b","9"],"¶Take thou also unto thee wheat, and barley, and beans, and lentiles, and millet, and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"fitches"],", and put them in one vessel, and make thee bread thereof,",["i","according"],"to the number of the days that thou shalt lie upon thy side, three hundred and ninety days shalt thou eat thereof."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/4.10","order":"02.27.004.55175"},["b","10"],"And thy",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"meat"],"which thou shalt eat",["i","shall be"],"by weight, twenty shekels a day: from time to time shalt thou eat it."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/4.11","order":"02.27.004.55176"},["b","11"],"Thou shalt drink also water by measure, the sixth part of an hin: from time to time shalt thou drink."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/4.12","order":"02.27.004.55177"},["b","12"],"And thou shalt eat it",["i","as"],"barley cakes, and thou shalt bake it with dung that cometh out of man, in their sight."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/4.13","order":"02.27.004.55178"},["b","13"],"And the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"said, Even thus shall the children of Israel eat their",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"defiled"],"bread among the Gentiles, whither I will drive them."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/4.14","order":"02.27.004.55179"},["b","14"],"Then said I, Ah Lord",["span.smallCaps","God"],"! behold, my soul hath not been",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"polluted"],": for from my youth up even till now have I not eaten of that which",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_14b"},"dieth"],"of itself, or is",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_14c"},"torn"],"in pieces; neither came there",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_14d"},"abominable"],"flesh into my mouth."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/4.15","order":"02.27.004.55180"},["b","15"],"Then he said unto me, Lo, I have given thee cow’s dung for man’s dung, and thou shalt prepare thy bread therewith."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/4.16","order":"02.27.004.55181"},["b","16"],"Moreover he said unto me, Son of man, behold, I will break the staff of bread in Jerusalem: and they shall eat bread by weight, and with care; and they shall drink water by measure, and with",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"astonishment"],":"],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/4.17","order":"02.27.004.55182"},["b","17"],"That they may want bread and water, and be",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"astonied"],"one with another, and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_17b"},"consume"],"away for their iniquity."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/4.1a","order":"02.27.004.55183"},["b","1a"],["span.small","IE"],"a clay tablet."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/4.1b","order":"02.27.004.55185"},["b","1b"],["span.small","IE"],"engrave or cut in it a representation of the city."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/4.2a","order":"02.27.004.55187"},["b","2a"],["span.small","IE"],"draw upon it the plan of the attack against the city."],["div",{"id":"2b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/4.2b","order":"02.27.004.55189"},["b","2b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/25.1"},"2 Kgs. 25:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"2c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/4.2c","order":"02.27.004.55191"},["b","2c"],["span.small","OR"],"build up a mound or bank."],["div",{"id":"2d","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/4.2d","order":"02.27.004.55193"},["b","2d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/6.6"},"Jer. 6:6"],"."],["div",{"id":"2e","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/4.2e","order":"02.27.004.55195"},["b","2e"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/21.22"},"Ezek. 21:22"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/4.3a","order":"02.27.004.55197"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/25.9"},"2 Ne. 25:9"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/4.9a","order":"02.27.004.55199"},["b","9a"],["span.small","OR"],"spelt (a type of wheat)."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/4.10a","order":"02.27.004.55201"},["b","10a"],["span.small","HEB"],"food."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/4.13a","order":"02.27.004.55203"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/9.3.1-3"},"Hosea 9:3 (1–3)"],"."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/4.14a","order":"02.27.004.55205"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/pollution"},"TG Pollution"],"."],["div",{"id":"14b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/4.14b","order":"02.27.004.55207"},["b","14b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lev/7.24"},"Lev. 7:24"],"."],["div",{"id":"14c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/4.14c","order":"02.27.004.55209"},["b","14c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/22.31"},"Ex. 22:31"],"."],["div",{"id":"14d","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/4.14d","order":"02.27.004.55211"},["b","14d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lev/7.18"},"Lev. 7:18"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lev/19.7"},"19:7"],"."],["div",{"id":"16a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/4.16a","order":"02.27.004.55213"},["b","16a"],["span.small","IE"],"fearfulness, anxiety."],["div",{"id":"17a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/4.17a","order":"02.27.004.55215"},["b","17a"],["span.small","HEB"],"appalled."],["div",{"id":"17b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/4.17b","order":"02.27.004.55217"},["b","17b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/12.3"},"Hel. 12:3"],"."]]}
